snippet.title: Dungelot: Shattered Lands Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Get it on Steam - http://store.steampowered.com/app/403940/ 
Get it on iOS - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/dungelot-shattered-lands/id1034658841?ls=1&mt=8
Android - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.redwinter.dungelot&hl=en


Dungelot: Shattered Lands is a Minesweeper-esque roguelike, packed with gurgling enemies, wicked mushrooms, angry totems, and a quite insane zombie cow. What what, Dungelot?
